	Infrastructure, Mass Transit and Veterans top the list.  Digital TV coupons are the least popular.
</div>
January 28th, 2pm ET
<p>
As the House gets set to vote on the stimulus plan, please also take the time to consider what the American people want.  Here is <a href="http://whitehouse2.org/issues/stimulus-package/official">President Official's plan</a>, ranked by thousands of citizens at <a href="http://whitehouse2.org/">WhiteHouse2.org</a>.  
<p>
